org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord
Interface IAeRegistrationRequest

All Known Implementing Classes:
AeRegistrationRequest
public interface IAeRegistrationRequest

Interface for a WS-Coordination registation request. Note: This is an internal implementation tailored to be used with requirement 111 i.e. the interface provides a simple property getter and setter. The final implementation should follow something close to the Register definition as per http://schemas.xmlsoap.org/ws/2004/10/wsoor. Maybe refactor this interface to wsio.IWebServiceCoordRegistrationRequest.
